## Performance Optimization

### Parallel Execution
```python
# Good: Process items in parallel
results = await asyncio.gather(*[
    process_item(item) for item in items
])

# Bad: Sequential processing
results = []
for item in items:
    result = await process_item(item)
    results.append(result)
```

